{"tid":265060,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實行山勁等唔等於長跑勁？","createTime":"2017-05-31T10:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T11:08:25.000Z","uid":117628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df801fa7b225334ea49c761f8516e47623d0903d","tid":265060,"uid":117628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:53:55.000Z","msg":"兩者性質類似，都係長時間運動，都需要體能同耐力，主要都係需要腳部既力量"},{"pid":"8eaa38f6b3cf7633f656f10b484470dab951d963","tid":265060,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"我行開山 但長跑真心一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n速度明顯比其他人慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時，長跑開既人行山未必勁<br />\n你睇下香港馬拉松出西隧口（好接近山路坡度）幾多人頂唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n長跑同行山其實點都有分別"},{"pid":"2bee05f5e6e5c8aa784d42ae35fa13ed57021758","tid":265060,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T11:02:30.000Z","msg":"唔關事，要講嘅所謂行山勁都有好多唔同種勁，有人長斜勁，有人上梯級勁，有人落山勁"},{"pid":"b12137f6b6f106bb34afdfcf5f549ae56632c705","tid":265060,"uid":22913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T11:04:01.000Z","msg":"跑山個d就真係勁"},{"pid":"ea23e79973fa7d730870fd67c75382db97daa817","tid":265060,"uid":13625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T11:08:25.000Z","msg":"行山=負重步行<br />\n長跑=空裝競速<br />\n<br />\n點都唔同<br />\n<br />\n但你玩開其中一邊 體能好 玩其他運動點都易上手啲"}]}